data.name: POLIURETANE (PU) TRANSPARENT DRESSINGS
data.description:
## COMPOSITION
- 100% Polyurethane (PUR) Transparent film
- Transfer Paper
- Adhesive: Acrylic

## STERILIZATION
- Ethylene Oxide (EO) Sterile

## PRESENTATIONS
- Various Shapes and Finishes
- With and without Haemostatic Island

## PERFORMANCE
- Skin friendly
- Highly Transparent
- Hypoallergenic
- Strong hold without skin irritation (Latex-free)
